snippet: Cometh the hour, cometh the man -- Andy Murray proved himself the bastion of British tennis once again as he outclassed Canadian powerhouse Milos Raonic to claim a second Wimbledon title in masterful fashion on Sunday....
lead_paragraph: Cometh the hour, cometh the man -- Andy Murray proved himself the bastion of British tennis once again as he outclassed Canadian powerhouse Milos Raonic to claim a second Wimbledon title in masterful fashion on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Masterful Murray Delivers Again for Grateful Nation
headline.main: Masterful Murray Delivers Again for Grateful Nation
